{
  "stem": "7455.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And with it, the materials that my father saved, which we had for the custom-making suits, was burned out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Everything was gone which we could have had to survive later, for trading in for food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My father looked around, looked in the ruins.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then he went-- there was one side of the house, which was to the rear, and he looks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The upper level of the house collapsed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And because when my father supervised the house, he knew everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There were steel beams, so when it collapsed, that part of a cellar remained, didn't go through.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It did not go through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so my father goes around the bend, around the house, and he sees the wooden doors are there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He pries them open.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There are steps.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that part of a cellar is there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It's hot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It's impossible to go in, but it's there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And my father said, we may be able to live in it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Being that everything collapsed, we have a roof.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The metal from the roof caved in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Everything caved in on top.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But it was hot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We couldn't go in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So we slept for two nights in the garden, spread under the trees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My father's sister, Pearl, and Rachel-- Rojo-- came-- when it was quiet down-- came running, seeing if we were-- we are alive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "When they saw our house burned down, they cried.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But then they said, you are alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they said, look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They had apartments and children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We'll take Rosa.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We'll take Laura.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "A few children, they take to their house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And the other sister will take us where we would stay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And my father said, we have a boding-- we have a foreboding of what's coming.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We want to be toge-- together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We don't want to separate.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
